Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.02,0:00:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}The universe extends without bound. Within\N{\c&He1e1e1&}it, many stars are born, and then die.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.37,0:00:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}The Galaxy Railways... That is what\N{\c&He1e1e1&}carries the hopes and yearnings{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.31,0:00:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}of those who dream of\N{\c&He1e1e1&}traveling the sea of space.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.38,0:00:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}However, in some cases, the universe\N{\c&He1e1e1&}delivers a cruel fate to them, as well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.39,0:00:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Mother, look. There are a\N{\c&He1e1e1&}bunch of rocks flying this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.06,0:00:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.73,0:01:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.08,0:01:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.75,0:01:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Please calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.42,0:01:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The Galaxy Railways are\N{\c&He1e1e1&}protected by orbital shields,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.32,0:01:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}as well as magnetic barriers,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}so we are safe-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.43,0:01:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.10,0:01:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Galaxy Railways {\i1}No. 707{\i0} has\N{\c&He1e1e1&}come to an emergency stop!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.11,0:01:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}They're 3500 spacekilos from the\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Tabito star system. Signal Red!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.78,0:01:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Their orbital shields are severely damaged.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Full power to the magnetic barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.45,0:01:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Receiving request for SDF dispatch!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.78,0:01:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Please wait! I've identified a white hole\N{\c&He1e1e1&}4000 spacekilos from the Tabito system!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.45,0:01:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Gravitational levels rising.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}At this rate!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.12,0:02:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Dispatch the Space Defense\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Force Sirius Platoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.73,0:02:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Send them to the rescue at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}The gears of fate are in motion.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}There is no one who can stop them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.75,0:02:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}Mankind can only submit themselves\N{\c&He1e1e1&}to the flow of those gears.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.49,0:02:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}"Departure"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.77,0:02:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.77,0:02:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What is the Galaxy Railways\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Administration doing about this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.43,0:02:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Hurry up and save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.10,0:02:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Ladies and gentlemen,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}I've just received word
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.90,0:02:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}that a rescue team has been dispatched.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.11,0:02:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}And so, I ask that you please calm\N{\c&He1e1e1&}down and return to your seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.78,0:02:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You expect us to relax and sit down!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Don't be ridiculous!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}We've got injured people here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.11,0:02:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It sounds like the SDF has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.05,0:03:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We will now start rescuing\N{\c&He1e1e1&}the passengers of {\i1}No. 707{\i0}.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.69,0:03:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}All hands, give me your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.39,0:03:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.80,0:03:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Let me go! Let me go! That\N{\c&He1e1e1&}hurts! Come on, let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.73,0:03:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Get in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.74,0:03:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I discovered these stowaways\N{\c&He1e1e1&}in the rear hangar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.07,0:03:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}They say they're with you,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain Yuuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.74,0:03:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You two!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.74,0:03:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.74,0:03:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We're sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.08,0:03:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain, they are your sons?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.75,0:03:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.42,0:03:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We're sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We didn't mean for this to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.09,0:03:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Dad, I want to help you out in your work!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.42,0:03:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Isn't there anything I can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.82,0:03:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Let me join the force!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.49,0:03:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Ah, that's mine. Thank you, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.44,0:04:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Make sure you don't lose it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.78,0:04:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain Yuuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.45,0:04:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}This person is the last of the passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.78,0:04:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}All right, mission accomplished.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.45,0:04:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.12,0:04:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You've been a great help to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.79,0:04:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We will tow {\i1}No. 707{\i0} to\N{\c&He1e1e1&}the nearest station.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.13,0:04:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm most grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.46,0:04:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Dad is so cool, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.13,0:04:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.80,0:04:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Ah, Captain! We have an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.47,0:04:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.47,0:04:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}There is an object appearing\N{\c&He1e1e1&}out of the white hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.81,0:04:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.15,0:04:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Hyperthermal matter approaching!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Range, 3000 spacekilos!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.49,0:04:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Hurry! Get us moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.17,0:05:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Attack evaded!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.50,0:05:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Forget about towing {\i1}No. 707{\i0}!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.44,0:05:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The lives of the passengers\N{\c&He1e1e1&}have top priority!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.77,0:05:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Request permission to return fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.44,0:05:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}If they pursue, you have permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.44,0:05:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.11,0:05:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Enemy approaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Prepare to fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.78,0:05:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Drop orbital shields! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.12,0:05:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu! Mamoru! Get away from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.79,0:05:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}D- Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.13,0:05:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It's all right. No worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.16,0:06:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}Big One?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.43,0:06:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}No doubt about it! That's... Augh-!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Dad has come home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.44,0:06:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm off to make a delivery!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.78,0:06:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Mamoru! Attaboy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.78,0:06:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.12,0:06:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Oiwa-{\i1}san{\i0}!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.45,0:06:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Your delivery!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.45,0:06:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Oh, Mamoru! Over here, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.79,0:06:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That was quick, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.13,0:06:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Oiwa-{\i1}san{\i0}, you sure eat a lot, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.46,0:06:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.46,0:06:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Come to think of it, Mamoru, what are you\N{\c&He1e1e1&}going to do once you graduate from school?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.47,0:06:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The SDF? I'm right, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.81,0:06:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Outer space, huh? If only I\N{\c&He1e1e1&}were 30 years younger, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.09,0:07:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Brother! Brother Mamoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.09,0:07:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Big One{\i0} is here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.10,0:07:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Dad's train is home!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It wasn't scheduled to be. Besides, Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.77,0:07:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Let's go see!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.77,0:07:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We can't! The train station has a rule\N{\c&He1e1e1&}that you can't get in without a pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.44,0:07:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Rules, rules, so what? Brother,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}you take things too seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.45,0:07:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.78,0:07:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Tell Mom I'll be home right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.12,0:07:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Piece of cake, piece of cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.13,0:07:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I don't have to have\N{\c&He1e1e1&}anything to do with passes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.81,0:07:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The Space Defense Force coach will\N{\c&He1e1e1&}be arriving shortly on Track 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.48,0:07:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Track 3?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.15,0:08:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.79,0:08:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.46,0:08:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Identifying intruder.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Don't shoot! Don't shoot!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}I just came to greet my dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What's the commotion?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.47,0:08:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}An intruder.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:08:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It looks like my son has\N{\c&He1e1e1&}been causing trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.14,0:09:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.41,0:09:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu, don't be so reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.41,0:09:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Thanks for coming to meet me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.75,0:09:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Say, Dad, how long can\N{\c&He1e1e1&}you stay this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.43,0:09:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You're leaving again right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.09,0:09:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.76,0:09:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It's your job, so it\N{\c&He1e1e1&}can't be helped, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.43,0:09:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Don't be so sassy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.10,0:09:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I do have one favor to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.10,0:09:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.10,0:09:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Let me ride on {\i1}Big One{\i0}.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.44,0:09:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.44,0:09:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.78,0:09:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It's against the rules. I can't let\N{\c&He1e1e1&}any unauthorized persons on the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.45,0:09:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Then I'll become a member\N{\c&He1e1e1&}of the Space Defense Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.88,0:09:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Then I could ride on it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.12,0:09:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.45,0:09:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Hey, even better!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.46,0:09:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm going to be a captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.12,0:09:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}When I grow up, I'm going to be a\N{\c&He1e1e1&}captain in the Space Defense Force!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.81,0:10:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Shutaro, how have you been doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.81,0:10:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Come on in-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.15,0:10:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.15,0:10:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu, where have you been?\N{\c&He1e1e1&}I was worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.15,0:10:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Kanna...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.49,0:10:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.82,0:10:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.16,0:10:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Mom's blushing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.83,0:10:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Now, look, Manabu-!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.83,0:10:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.83,0:10:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Brother! It was Dad's {\i1}Big One{\i0}, all right!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.50,0:10:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Mamoru, have you been doing okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.17,0:10:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Dad, welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.17,0:10:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.17,0:10:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Say, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.18,0:10:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Let's play some catch!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}That's okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.85,0:10:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Okay? Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.51,0:10:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.85,0:10:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}All right, how about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.85,0:10:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Nice ball! Manabu, you've gotten so\N{\c&He1e1e1&}you can throw a ball pretty well, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.86,0:11:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I've been practicing\N{\c&He1e1e1&}every day with Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Is that right? Mamoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.47,0:11:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm not going to lag\N{\c&He1e1e1&}behind you any more, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.47,0:11:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}How about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.14,0:11:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yowch! Mamoru, you're incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.81,0:11:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Brother, that was cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.48,0:11:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Your Dad is getting too old for this.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}You two keep going by yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.81,0:11:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Huh? How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.82,0:11:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Is the captain being a sore loser?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.82,0:11:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Let me spend some time\N{\c&He1e1e1&}with your mom, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.82,0:11:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Eh, how boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.82,0:11:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu, let's play.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.83,0:11:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}A job well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.49,0:11:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}They sure are getting bigger,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}aren't they? Both of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.50,0:11:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.50,0:11:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Brother, here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.50,0:11:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Not bad, Manabu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.84,0:11:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Thanks. This is all\N{\c&He1e1e1&}because of you, Kanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.46,0:12:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Understood. I'll leave right away.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Assemble the platoon at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.79,0:12:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}A scramble?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.13,0:12:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Sorry. They said there was a train near\N{\c&He1e1e1&}this planet that was at a standstill.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.13,0:12:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'll tell the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.14,0:12:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Kanna, I'm sorry about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.80,0:12:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.81,0:12:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It's a little early, but here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.81,0:12:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.48,0:12:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Your birthday present.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.82,0:12:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Thanks. Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.49,0:12:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Come back soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.49,0:12:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.83,0:12:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Nice work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.50,0:12:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.84,0:12:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.84,0:12:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Going to the bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.51,0:12:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Not dressed like that, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.85,0:13:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I- I want to go see Dad off!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Please, let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.78,0:13:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.12,0:13:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.79,0:13:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.46,0:13:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It's all right. This way, this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.79,0:13:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I can't keep up that fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.13,0:13:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We of the Sirius Platoon\N{\c&He1e1e1&}have an emergency mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.80,0:13:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Everyone see to your stations,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.13,0:13:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}and await our departure order.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.47,0:13:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That is all. Prepare to get underway!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.14,0:13:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The gravity barrier shows no problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.81,0:13:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Pressure is building within the boiler.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.48,0:13:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}All right, we're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Hurry and get up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.15,0:13:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Brother! Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.82,0:13:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Let's go look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.50,0:13:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}So this is Dad's train?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.50,0:13:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I wonder if Dad has\N{\c&He1e1e1&}gotten aboard already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.17,0:13:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Intruders sighted! Intruders sighted!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.50,0:13:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu, this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.51,0:14:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Energy at normal. Pressure\N{\c&He1e1e1&}is rising within the boiler.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.44,0:14:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Cylinder valves open.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Main circuits engaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.12,0:14:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Systems all green!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.12,0:14:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Brother, we've had it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.45,0:14:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Hang in there, Manabu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.45,0:14:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Right, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Move out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.15,0:14:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}This can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.15,0:14:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We've started moving.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}What do we do, Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It's too late now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.83,0:15:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Outer space...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.44,0:15:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.44,0:15:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu! Manabu, stay with me! Manabu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.78,0:15:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.78,0:15:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Have you come around?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.78,0:15:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Are you both all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.78,0:15:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.12,0:15:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}But Dad, you're hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.12,0:15:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Don't worry about your dad. Manabu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.46,0:15:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Uh-huh, I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.13,0:15:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You're pretty strong. You are\N{\c&He1e1e1&}your father's sons, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.47,0:15:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.47,0:15:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Five minutes until the enemy\N{\c&He1e1e1&}ship completes "hole-out."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.47,0:15:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}No! Don't let them out, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.47,0:15:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.81,0:15:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain, you're injured!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.81,0:15:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.48,0:15:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Launch all fighters!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.11,0:16:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}All fighters have been lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.11,0:16:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The battle car has been demolished!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.78,0:16:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Closing bulkheads.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.45,0:16:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bulkhead lockdown complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.45,0:16:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Three minutes to hole-out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.12,0:16:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}If this keeps up...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Incoming!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.46,0:16:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Full power to magnetic shields!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.13,0:16:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}There's not enough time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.14,0:16:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.48,0:16:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Don't worry, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.81,0:16:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'll make sure you\N{\c&He1e1e1&}get back to your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.82,0:16:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.82,0:16:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.82,0:17:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}All of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.42,0:17:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We're going to show what the Space\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Defense Force is really made of!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.09,0:17:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.43,0:17:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}As of now, I'm transferring command\N{\c&He1e1e1&}over Sirius Platoon to Schwanheld Bulge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.10,0:17:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}- Please, wait, Captain! You can't-\N{\c&He1e1e1&}- Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.10,0:17:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}All hands, move to the passenger cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.30,0:17:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Big One{\i0} will act as a lure\N{\c&He1e1e1&}to draw the enemy away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.77,0:17:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You will use auxiliary power to clear the\N{\c&He1e1e1&}battle area, and wait for reinforcements.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.78,0:17:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What about you, Dad?\N{\c&He1e1e1&}What's going to happen to you, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.45,0:17:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Dad, answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.45,0:17:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Mamoru, it's about time\N{\c&He1e1e1&}you were considering
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.79,0:17:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}what course to take in life, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.12,0:17:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}No matter what anyone else tells\N{\c&He1e1e1&}you, you do what you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.79,0:17:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Your life belongs to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.80,0:17:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.80,0:17:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu, listen close to\N{\c&He1e1e1&}what your brother says,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.14,0:17:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}and help your mom out for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.81,0:17:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.81,0:17:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Why are you saying such things!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.81,0:17:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.81,0:18:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.48,0:18:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}All hands, move to the\N{\c&He1e1e1&}rear decks at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.75,0:18:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bulge...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.42,0:18:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm counting on you to see this through.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.09,0:18:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Salute Captain Yuuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.43,0:18:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.43,0:18:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}Mamoru... Manabu...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.11,0:18:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Dad! Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.78,0:18:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}My sons, once you become adults, and\N{\c&He1e1e1&}set forth across this vast sea of space,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.78,0:18:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}think of your father, and\N{\c&He1e1e1&}show me your valiant spirits.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.12,0:18:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.79,0:18:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.80,0:18:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}One minute to hole-out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.41,0:19:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Maximum pressure on the cylinders!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Target the enemy ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.08,0:19:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.76,0:19:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Kanna, this time, it looks like\N{\c&He1e1e1&}I will be gone a long while...
